        "title": "[codex] Add local ClawSweeper review workflow",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds a local ClawSweeper review workflow for maintainers who want advisory output before PR submission or re-review. This was based on a discussion with @joshavant on Discord.\n\n## Changes\n\n- Add `pnpm run review -- --local-only` for read-only local issue/PR review without the starter GitHub comment.\n- Add `pnpm run codex:local:check` to verify local Codex CLI auth and execution without printing secrets.\n- Preserve local Codex auth only for `--local-only`; hosted/normal workers still strip Codex/OpenAI/GitHub write credentials.\n- Prefer the Windows Codex app binary for local-only review and support Node-shebang Codex shims on Windows.\n- Add `.agents/skills/local-clawsweeper-review` as an optional ergonomic Codex wrapper.\n- Add `docs/local-clawsweeper-review.md`, including one-PR-at-a-time setup, CLI auth, clean target checkout guidance, managed checkout behavior, and embedded optional skill contents.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `pnpm run check`\n- Final-head Codex preflight on `878702947358b6ae5f08767da52904c7b93a015f`:\n\n```text\npnpm run codex:local:check\n\nCodex binary: codex\nChecking Codex login status...\nChecking Codex login status completed in 0.1s.\nRunning Codex smoke test with gpt-5.5...\nRunning Codex smoke test with gpt-5.5 completed in 32.8s.\nCodex local preflight passed.\n```\n\n- Final-head local review proof on `878702947358b6ae5f08767da52904c7b93a015f`:\n\n```text\npnpm run review -- --local-only --target-repo openclaw/clawsweeper --item-number 357 --artifact-dir artifacts/local-review-357-final-proof\n\nLocal ClawSweeper review for openclaw/clawsweeper#357\n\nPreparing target checkout\n  mode: managed PR checkout\n  path: artifacts/local-review-357-final-proof/target\n  base: main\n\nLoading review item\n  item: PR #357\n  title: [codex] Add local ClawSweeper review workflow\n  state: open\n\nCollecting GitHub context\n\nRunning Codex review\n  timeout: 20m 0s\n  stdout: artifacts/local-review-357-final-proof/codex/357.1.codex.stdout.log\n  stderr: artifacts/local-review-357-final-proof/codex/357.1.codex.stderr.log\n\nReview complete\n  elapsed: 2m 33s\n  decision: keep_open\n  confidence: high\n  action: kept_open\n  report: artifacts/local-review-357-final-proof/357.md\n```\n\nLocal review artifact summary:\n\n- `review_status=complete`\n- `decision=keep_open`\n- `confidence=high`\n- `action_taken=kept_open`\n- `review_service_tier=fast`\n- `local_checkout_access=verified`\n- `main_sha=bd03fe34c0a49e17735186bc15e6e8656d03e2e2`\n- `pull_head_sha=878702947358b6ae5f08767da52904c7b93a015f`\n- Managed target checkout remained clean after the run: `## clawsweeper/pr-357`\n\nNo GitHub apply/close command was run; this was local-only advisory review proof.",
